'''Yin Wood Pig also known as äđäšĨ''' (kinotoi (äđäšĨ), otsubokunoinoshishi (äđäšĨ), itsugai (äđäšĨ)) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|å­ååđēæŊ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 12th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|å­ååđēæŊ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Jikotsu|ja|1=Yang Wood Dog|2=ja|įēæ|lt=Jikotsu|lt_ja=įēæ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jikotsu|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Besshi|ja|1=Yang Fire Rat|2=ja|äļå­|1=Yang Fire Rat|lt=Besshi|lt_ja=äļå­|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Besshi|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|é°é―äščĄææģ|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=é°é―äščĄ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|qq=}}, the element represented by the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|ååđē|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Etsu|ja|äđ|1=Kinoto (äđ)|lt=Kinoto (äđ)|2=ja|3=äđ|4=zh|5=äđ|1=Kinoto (äđ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Etsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (äđ)|qq=}} signifies yin {{ill|Wood|ja|æĻ|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (æĻ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood|qq=}}, while the element represented by the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|åäšæŊ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Pig|ja|äšĨ|1=Pig (Zodiac)|lt=Pig (äšĨ)|2=ja|3=äšĨ|1=Pig (zodiac)|lt=Pig (äšĨ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Pig|13=User:Immanuelle/Pig (zodiac)|qq=}} signifies yin {{ill|Water|zh|Water (æ°ī)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=ÐÐūÐīÐ° (ÐĢ-ŅŅÐ―)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische FÃžmf-ElemÃĪnt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Tháŧ§y (NgÅĐ hÃ nh)|10=pt|11=Ãgua (astrologia)|lt=Water (æ°ī)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=ÐÐūÐīÐ° (ÐĢ-ŅŅÐ―)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische FÃžmf-ElemÃĪnt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Tháŧ§y (NgÅĐ hÃ nh)|10=pt|11=Ãgua (astrologia)|lt=Water (æ°ī)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=ÐÐūÐīÐ° (ÐĢ-ŅŅÐ―)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische FÃžmf-ElemÃĪnt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Tháŧ§y (NgÅĐ hÃ nh)|10=pt|11=Ãgua (astrologia)|lt=Water (æ°ī)|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=ÐÐūÐīÐ° (ÐĢ-ŅŅÐ―)|lt=Water (æ°ī)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=ÐÐūÐīÐ° (ÐĢ-ŅŅÐ―)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische FÃžmf-ElemÃĪnt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Tháŧ§y (NgÅĐ hÃ nh)|10=pt|11=Ãgua (astrologia)|lt=Water (æ°ī)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water|qq=}}, establishing a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|äščĄææģ#įļįïžãããããïž|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=įļį|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=}}, i.e. Water generates Wood).

