== Month of Etsugai (äđäšĨãŪæ) ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|čĨŋæĶ|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=čĨŋæĶ|4=zh|5=åŽå|6=es|7=Era comÃšn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (corresponding to the heavenly stems {{ill|Kou|ja|įē|1=Kinoe (įē)|lt=Kinoe (įē)|2=ja|3=įē|4=zh|5=įē|1=Kinoe (įē)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (įē)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (įē)|qq=}} or {{ill|Ki|ja|å·ą|1=Tsuchinoto (å·ą)|lt=Tsuchinoto (å·ą)|2=ja|3=å·ą|4=zh|5=å·ą|1=Tsuchinoto (å·ą)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (å·ą)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (å·ą)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|October|ja|10æ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October|qq=}} is designated as the Etsugai {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|æ (æĶ)|lt=Month|lt_ja=æ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|æ§æĶ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Beginning of Winter|ja|įŦåŽ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Winter|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Winter|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Heavy Snow|ja|åĪ§éŠ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavy Snow|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavy Snow|qq=}}) as applicable.

