'''Yin Wood Pig also known as äđäšĨ''' (kinotoi (äđäšĨ), otsubokunoinoshishi (äđäšĨ), itsugai (äđäšĨ)) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|å­ååđēæŊ|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to åđēæŊ|1=Sexagenary cycle|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q246658}}.

It is the 12th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|å­ååđēæŊ|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to åđēæŊ|1=Sexagenary cycle|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q246658}}, preceded by {{ill|Jikotsu|ja|1=Yang Wood Dog|2=ja|įēæ|lt=Jikotsu|lt_ja=įēæ|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jikotsu|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jikotsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Wood Dog|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} and followed by {{ill|Besshi|ja|1=Yang Fire Rat|2=ja|äļå­|1=Yang Fire Rat|lt=Besshi|lt_ja=äļå­|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Besshi|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Besshi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Rat|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|é°é―äščĄææģ|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=é°é―äščĄ|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the element represented by the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|en|Heavenly Stems|WD=Q1190985|lt=Heavenly Stems|1=Heavenly Stems}} symbol {{ill|Etsu|ja|äđ|1=Kinoto (äđ)|lt=Kinoto (äđ)|2=ja|3=äđ|4=zh|5=äđ|1=Kinoto (äđ)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Etsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (äđ)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Etsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (äđ)|qq=}} signifies yin {{ill|Wood|ja|Wood (æĻ)|1=Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (æĻ)|2=uk|3=ÐÐĩŅÐĩÐēÐū (ÐĩÐŧÐĩÐžÐĩÐ―Ņ)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Máŧc (NgÅĐ hÃ nh)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=āŪŪāŪ°āŪŪāŊ (āŪāŊāŪĐ āŪŪāŊāŪŊāŊāŪŊāŪŋāŪŊāŪēāŊ)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (æĻ)|lt=Wood (æĻ)|2=uk|3=ÐÐĩŅÐĩÐēÐū (ÐĩÐŧÐĩÐžÐĩÐ―Ņ)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xin